### ==================== AUTH ROUTES ====================

### 1. Register User (Do this first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jon Doe",
  "email": "jon@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "admin",
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210"
}

### 2. Login User (Do this second - Copy the token from response and paste it in @token above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jon@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Pending Users (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Approve User (Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/auth/approve/userId123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==================== STUDENT ROUTES ====================

### Get Student Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/students/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Student Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/students/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "cgpa": 8.5,
  "branch": "Computer Science",
  "backlogs": 0,
  "skills": ["JavaScript", "React", "Node.js"]
}

### Get All Students (Admin, Coordinator, Company Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Upload Resume
POST {{baseUrl}}/students/resume
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resume"; filename="resume.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

<@resume.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Get Eligible Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/students/eligible-jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==================== COMPANY ROUTES ====================

### Get Company Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/companies/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Company Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/companies/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Tech Corp",
  "location": "Bangalore",
  "description": "Leading tech company",
  "website": "https://techcorp.com"
}

### Get All Companies (Admin, Coordinator Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/companies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Post a Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/companies/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobTitle": "Senior Developer",
  "description": "We are looking for a senior developer",
  "location": "Bangalore",
  "salary": {
    "min": 600000,
    "max": 1000000
  },
  "requirements": {
    "minCGPA": 7.0,
    "backlogs": 0,
    "skills": ["JavaScript", "React", "Node.js"]
  },
  "applyBy": "2026-06-30"
}

### Get Posted Jobs for Company
GET {{baseUrl}}/companies/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Job
PUT {{baseUrl}}/companies/jobs/jobId123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobTitle": "Senior Developer",
  "description": "Updated job description",
  "salary": {
    "min": 700000,
    "max": 1200000
  }
}


### ==================== JOB ROUTES ====================

### Get All Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Job by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/jobId123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==================== APPLICATION ROUTES ====================

### Apply to Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/applications/apply/jobId123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coverLetter": "I am interested in this position"
}

### Get Applications for Job (Company, Coordinator, Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/applications/job/jobId123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Student Applications
GET {{baseUrl}}/applications/my-applications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Application Status (Company, Coordinator, Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/applications/applicationId123/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "selected"
}


### ==================== INTERVIEW ROUTES ====================

### Schedule Interview (Company, Coordinator, Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/interviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicationId": "appId123",
  "scheduledDate": "2026-06-15",
  "scheduledTime": "10:30",
  "interviewType": "technical",
  "round": 1
}

### Get Student Interviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/interviews/my-interviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Job Interviews (Company, Coordinator, Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/interviews/job/jobId123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Interview (Company, Coordinator, Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/interviews/interviewId123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed",
  "result": "passed",
  "feedback": "Candidate performed well"
}


### ==================== ANALYTICS ROUTES ====================

### Get Admin Dashboard Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Company Dashboard Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/company
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==================== NOTIFICATION ROUTES ====================

### Get My Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark Notification as Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/notificationId123/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark All Notifications as Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==================== ATTENDANCE ROUTES ====================

### Record Attendance (Admin, Coordinator Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "studentId123",
  "eventId": "eventId123",
  "eventName": "Company Recruitment Drive",
  "attended": true
}

### Get Attendance by Event (Admin, Coordinator, Company Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/event
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Student Attendance
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/student/studentId123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


